<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">الله تعالى:</span> وَلاكِنّاا حُمِّلْناا أَوْزااراً مِنْ زِينَةِ الْقَوْمِ <span class="c2">«١»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وحمّله حاجته:</span> أي سأله القيامَ بها.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
