<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span><span class="c4">[الاحتماء]</span>: احتمى من الطعام وغيره.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span><span class="c5">والاحتماء:</span> الامتناع.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
